<TEXT>
<P>
 Your July 10 Style layout, "Grandes Dames," had the most beautiful photographs 
that I have ever seen in a newspaper. I found it hard to believe that these 
were photographs and not actual paintings. The impact of these re-creations of 
the great paintings was so electric that, in my opinion, they constitute great 
works of art themselves. 
</P>
<P>
 BETTY FREEMAN 
