LOVE THAT LARROQUETTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I would rather see a rerun of "The John Larroquette Show" than a premiere of a 
new series.The show is so superior to the many others with higher ratings, 
which I can't understand. 
</P>
<P>
 The writing, directing and supporting cast are excellent. The show is so real. 
I have had real "out loud" laughs while watching this show and, in the same 
half hour, tears. Please keep the show on, NBC. John Larroquette is superb. 
</P>
<P>
 Charlene E. Lynn, Van Nuys  
