<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAWYER'S SAWBUCKS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding Jane Hall's "The PrimeTime of Ms. Diane Sawyer" (Aug. 7), the 
question is posed: "Does Diane Sawyer deserve her $7-million contract with ABC 
News?" The answer is yes, and no.Yes, because anyone who can manage to extract 
such a ridiculously huge sum from the coffers of the lunatics who run ABC 
obviously deserves it. And no, because Sawyer is no more talented than 
thousands of other broadcasters doing the same thing every day without the 
media hype/fanfare provided by ABC promotion. And she admits this in the 
article. I hope this answers your question! 
</P>
<P>
 LAWRENCE M. KATES 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
