FACTS FOR FIDO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Vacationing With Your Pet!" by Eileen Barish is a book every pet owner who 
travels should have.You can order it from Pet Friendly Publications at (800) 
496-2665. It's $14.95 plus $3.75 shipping and handling (and worth every 
penny!). After years of hassles and numerous arguments about where I could stay 
with my dog, this book makes traveling simple. I highly recommend it. 
</P>
<P>
 NONA SUE FRIEDMAN, Los Angeles 
