<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITIZENS SEEKING STRONGER VOICE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I am responding to a letter ("Possible Jail Expansion," Aug. 2).Other cities 
are experiencing lack of control over their community. 
</P>
<P>
 We, the citizens of Buena Park, urged our City Council to give us a "right to 
vote" on putting our Fire Department under the county's regionalization; we 
were flatly denied the constitutional right. Consequently, Buena Park lost its 
Fire Department. 
</P>
<P>
 For this reason, some citizens here in Buena Park have ordered a committee 
called Voters in Action (VIA) to initiate a referendum to correct some of the 
inadequacies in local government. Other cities have formed similar committees. 
</P>
<P>
 It is a start in the right direction. 
</P>
<P>
 MARILYN KIETZMAN 
</P>
<P>
 Buena Park 
</P>
</TEXT>
