Candidate Has Foes in Her Own Party," July 31) follows this trend and continues 
to worry me about the party's prospects in 1994 and 1996.The squabbles come 
about at the worst possible time because, thanks to the President, we have a 
golden opportunity to take control of both the state Legislature and Congress 
within the next two election cycles. 
</P>
<P>
