</P>
<P>
 Ventura County schools have classes as big or bigger than the state average. 
And at most county schools, classes have increased in size over the past five 
years. The following average class sizes, shown from biggest to smallest, were 
compiled by the state Department of Education. But local school officials say 
many classes are actually much larger. 
</P>
